{"tid":1444394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣坐左成日都無人理, 黑警都唔係傻","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:06:02.000Z","uid":11454,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e98b9370b4fc7f9b5692e8a296ffaf4f0117d407","tid":1444394,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣仲有手足坐係sogo出面坐緊<br />\n計埋今日已經試左幾次無人理<br />\n得一次有TG, 其他係無狗出現過, 知唔知點解?<br />\n<br />\n因為銅鑼灣無狗屋, 無目標<br />\n遊客區, 鏡頭影到唔好睇<br />\n多人多商場, 入左室內, D狗冇得玩<br />\n對於黑警黎講, 銅鑼灣係最低急切性<br />\n只要唔理, 最後都會尾班車走<br />\n<br />\n唔好再一相情願覺得銅鑼灣係重點"},{"pid":"70d91de321defe368fede9d700886d70a65f0a1f","tid":1444394,"uid":173286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"bdd3744125e25fbf0437f6b990585796c582d917","tid":1444394,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c5138a43f1eec6b8737315ba3a1af867c25a01","tid":1444394,"uid":76867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"咁遊客區係咪可以反而係果度派下文宣<br />\n輸出大陸睇唔到既資訊<br />\n做咩仲要等黑警黎"},{"pid":"51d2b3d72b8ef36d9881b5b142193847e2d348a2","tid":1444394,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e5d3415a4c5fcb394874dcea21c0d7ec9cafda93","tid":1444394,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3580f0122faaeec0cb8c616635a7eeed32d31f","tid":1444394,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal